{"word":"μεσόγεως","slug":"μεσόγεως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μεσόγεως</b></el> <el>(μεσόγεως, ων,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>attic for <a href='S:μεσόγαιος'><el>μεσόγαιος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><el>μεσόγεως</el> As <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a>, <el>μεσογαία</el>, <i>the inland parts, interior</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>loca mediterranea</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; so, <el>μεσογεία, ἡ</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}